---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'About Ibiza Cool Party – Your Ibiza Nightlife Guide',
  description: 'Ibiza Cool Party is your trusted guide to the island\'s best clubs, parties, hotels, and travel tips. Learn more about who we are.',
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 prose prose-invert">
    <h1>About Ibiza Cool Party</h1>
    <p>
      We're a team of Ibiza lovers dedicated to helping you plan the ultimate party trip to the White Isle.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether it's your first time or your tenth summer in Ibiza, we provide up-to-date, honest information about the island's clubs, boat parties, pool parties, hotels, and transfers — so you can spend less time planning and more time dancing.
    </p>
    <h2>What We Cover</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Clubs</strong> – In-depth guides to every major venue</li>
      <li><strong>Boat Parties</strong> – The best floating raves and sunset cruises</li>
      <li><strong>Hotels</strong> – Where to stay near the action</li>
      <li><strong>Transfers</strong> – Getting from A to B without the stress</li>
      <li><strong>Weekly Parties</strong> – What's on every night of the week</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Affiliate Partnerships</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on our site are affiliate links. This means we may earn a small commission when you book through us — at no extra cost to you. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">full disclosure</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
